Hello guys this is the very simple lab you just need to take care of one thing here. So let's get stared

Now look closely for vroot if its in sda then used or its is sdb 

For now it's in sda
 So we are using 

Until you get No partition yet please run that command other wise you won't get the score.

If you face any issue or have any doubt please comment we will help you :P



For SDA

lsblk

sudo fdisk /dev/sdb

d and 2 times enter button

 sudo mkfs -t ext4 /dev/sdb2
sudo mount /dev/sdb2 /home/my_drive


For SDB


lsblk

sudo fdisk /dev/sda

d and 2 times enter button

 sudo mkfs -t ext4 /dev/sda2
sudo mount /dev/sda2 /home/my_drive



